## Final Coverage

- 16 fuzzer harnesses (13 baseline + 3 gap fuzzers)
- 132+ seed files across 8 corpus directories + auth/blob/unicode
- ~135 MB total binary size
- 0 crashes
- All attack surfaces covered

### Phase 3: Seed Corpus (Complete)
- 131 seed files across 8 corpus directories
- XRPC, CBOR, HTTP, JWT, MST, SQL, MIME, Lexicon

### Phase 4: Custom Mutators (Complete)
- JWTMutator.mm - JWT segment-aware mutations
- HTTPMutator.mm - HTTP grammar mutations
- CBORMutator.mm - CBOR type mutations
- XrpcMutator.mm - JSON mutations

### Phase 5: Protocol Corpus (Complete)
- 38 XRPC test cases covering all major methods
- Session, Identity, Repo, Graph, Feed, Sync

### Phase 6: Coverage Instrumentation (Complete)
- FuzzCoverageTracker.m
- FUZZER_COVERAGE CMake option
- fuzzing-metrics.html dashboard

### Phase 7: CI Integration (Complete)
- .github/workflows/fuzzing.yml
- Daily schedule (2 AM UTC)
- Manual dispatch support

### Phase 8: Minimizer + Triage + Dictionaries (Complete)
- FuzzMinimizer.m
- minimize-corpus.sh
- triage-crashes.sh
- json.dict, cbor.dict, http.dict, jwt.dict

### Phase 9: Regression + Coverage Diff + Multi-path (Complete)
- regression-runner.sh
- coverage-diff.sh
- fuzz_multi_json (7 parsing paths)
- known-bad baseline

### Phase 10: Grammars + Sanitizers (Complete)
- json.dict, cbor.dict, http.dict grammars
- BUILD_FUZZERS_USE_MSAN option
- BUILD_FUZZERS_USE_UBSAN option

